ls 5;\n- Add support to `JSONAPI::Resources` at version `0.8.0.beta1`;\n- It no longer needs to inherit `JSONAPI::Resources` directly in controllers, only `JSONAPI::Utils` is required;\n- Lots of code refactoring.\n"}
